data.description: Great new Price 10K below Sept ’23 Appraisal.  +5K closing assist & 1 yr. POA dues credited at closing.  90day Contingency w/contract by 1/1/24.  Features Complete renovation 2022-23 including:  New Flooring/paint, Granite in baths/kitchen, New Roof 2021, New HVAC/Heating 2022, New Generac Generator 2022.  Two of the BR have private full baths, 2 Living spaces (one could be BR with private entrance from Garage or Deck), 2 workshops + Private office (1 Shop/Office in Oversized Att Garage/1 shop in new 24’x30’ Insulated shop with 220 elect, 9ft door) 2 propane tanks – 1 for Heat and 2nd for gas range and BBQ, Wrap around deck with Hot Tub.  Too many upgrades to mention including, Pull-out Storage/Trash in Kitchen, smart lighting with Bluetooth speakers and rock walks and landscaping.  All located short distance from private Golf Course, restaurant and river floating.  Private road with very little traffic.  Short commute to Tahlequah, Siloam Springs, Springdale/Rogers or Tulsa. Or work from home with Fiber Optic in your private office.
